* Fine-Grained Access\nwith Dynamic Views
** Recipient properties
***_ ALTER RECIPIENT SET PROPERTIES
***_ Key-value pairs (e.g., country_region)
** Row-level filtering
***_ WHERE region = CURRENT_RECIPIENT('property')
***_ Each recipient sees only their slice
** Column-level masking
***_ CASE WHEN CURRENT_RECIPIENT(...) = 'full'
***_ ELSE 'REDACTED'
***_ PII protection per recipient
** Partition filtering
***_ ALTER SHARE ... ADD TABLE
***_ PARTITION (col = CURRENT_RECIPIENT('prop'))
***_ No view needed for simple cases
** Testing
***_ Cannot query CURRENT_RECIPIENT() as provider
***_ Test by sharing with yourself as recipient
@endmindmap
